title: Euro Temptations Original Tracks v1.0 (incomplete)
description:
From DJ Inphinity&#039;s Euro Temptations 1-13, comes the original songs used in each of his mixes. Keep in mind that this list is, as for now, VERY limited (a lot of the songs are really rare, and very very difficult to find ANYWHERE), but compared to how many songs there should be, there are a decent amount of songs listed below that you&#039;ll find in this torrent. There&#039;s only about 15% of the songs listed in the torrent, but its 15% out of 450+ songs (about 70 songs). Also note that the songs each have a box next to them that looks either like a [ ], [x], or a [X]. The songs with an empty box are not in this torrent, the songs with a little "x" are in the torrrent, but are not the EXACT radio cut/remix used in DJ Inphinity&#039;s mixes (or I&#039;m not 100% that they are), and the songs with a large "X" next to them are the official song that DJ Inphinity used in his remix.

Keep in mind, there&#039;s a lot of empty boxes, and I hope that if you have a song that isn&#039;t listed below, then you can email me at <a class="__cf_email__" href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" data-cfemail="b4d7dcddd7dfd1dad0d5dad7d186f4dcdbc0d9d5ddd89ad7dbd9">[email&#160;protected]</a><script cf-hash='f9e31' type="text/javascript">
